### HYMN CXV

<span class="margnote"><span id="an_2011501">1</span></span>I from my
Father have received deep knowledge of the holy  
  Law:  
  I was born like unto the Sun.  
<span class="margnote"><span id="an_2011502">2</span></span>After the
lore of ancient time I make, like Kanva, beauteous  
   songs,  
  And Indra's self gains strength thereby.  
<span class="margnote"><span id="an_2011503">3</span></span>Whatever
Rishis have not praised thee, Indra, or have lauded  
   thee,  
  By me exalted wax thou strong.

